<HEADLINE>
IF BIOLOGY IS ANCESTRY, ARE THESE PEOPLE RELATED? 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating) 
 (ATTN: England)   (The Week in Review)  
 By NICHOLAS WADE   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   The crime scene was bare of clues. Even DNA fingerprinting
