<HEADLINE>
DOWN ABOUT THE COUNT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 By STEVEN A. HOLMES   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
