<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-10 13:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2274 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-JORDAN-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      04-10 0773
