   (Jodie T. Allen, former Washington editor of Slate, is a senior
writer at U.S. News &AMP; World Report)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BY JODIE T. ALLEN &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
