<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AIRLINE QUALITY FELL IN 1999, REPORT FINDS
 &HT;    450&AMP;add. With AIRLINE-DATA. Moving in (w) Washington and (f)
financial categories.
 &HT;    By ISMAIL TURAY Jr.
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox Newspapers
