</P>
<P>
   COXNET PTECH 0411 _ The Internet has become a valuable source of
information related to movies. Besides the obvious promotional Web
sites associated with Hollywood's studios, there are numerous sites
that compile and summarize film reviews from a variety of critics.
Here are a few. (Staff, Austin American-Statesman) Art includes an
attractive 4-column color iillustration of a drive-in with a
computer as a drive-in screen.
</P>
