<P>
   CHINESE-THEATER (Washington) _ Say Hello to Mann's Chinese
Theater _ in China. American movie companies could build theaters
in mainland China and retain nearly half the revenue from them
under a trade proposal, Motion Picture Association of America chief
Jack Valenti will tell senators on Tuesday. By Bill Hillburg. (Will
