<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-10 21:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2780 &Cx1f; tic-z
r l BC-AFGHAN-AZR &LR;      04-10 1153
