   (NYT37) WASHINGTON -- April 10, 2000 -- MICROSOFT-LOBBY -- Ralph
Reed's lobbying company has a new client: Microsoft. Reed is
quietly lobbying prominent supporters of George W. Bush to write
the Texas governor and probable Republican presidential candidate,
